race.description: The Country Club St Georges Basin Maiden Plate
race.comment: BOOM IN THE DARK (3) starting to hit his straps this prep. Shouldered the 60.5kg with a gritty on-pace second over 1200m at Moruya. Nick Heywood stays on and shapes as a genuine contender. SIR LUNCHALOTS (9) scored a decisive win two-back at Wagga, then folded up in the straight  with a dismal eighth over 1400m at the Sapphire Coast. Back in trip and should find this more to his liking. BRUTAL EYES (5) returns without a trial after going out a winner over the mile at Canberra last September. Placed fresh and proven at the trip. YOU WISH (7) won well two back at Albury before a 1.8L defeat at the Sapphire Coast most recently. Will handle the soggy deck and make her presence felt.
